{"type": "article", "id": 24080, "title": "放杂志的木篮", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-18T07:00:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 41, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702110331JBtSQdF0zoL3ru8A.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是一个放杂志的架子，它有一个像篮子一样的外形。上面是一个手提杆，而下面有两个小格子去放上几本杂志，整体保持对称的形态，简单优雅。这种设计增加了它的灵活性，你可以带着它从客厅到卧室，这种轻松的感觉与杂志正好很搭配。可以选择三种材料，红木、橡木和橡木和橄榄木的搭配。设计师来自米兰，他们做了很多类似的木质小家具，售价 200 美元，<a href=\"https://www.crowdyhouse.com/shop/gaetana-magazine-rack/\">这里是购买链接。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021103289825lTACH4cVWtOK.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021103289oCaLQTkxB6INr0M.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110329NH7YlyIeuLhrAqzJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67978723\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021103305FR2fPouy0A4MxN1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}